title: Haindava
overview: Haindava is a Telugu adventure thriller movie directed by Ludheer Byreddy. The movie casts Bellamkonda Sai Sreenivas in the main lead role. The music was composed by Leon James while the cinematography was done by Shivendra and it is edited by Karthika Srinivas R. The web series is produced by Mahesh Chandu under the Moonshine Pictures banner
